IParseText Interface

Definition

Defines methods for parsing text when JScript code is being authored in an editor.

In this Article

[System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComVisible(true)]
[System.Runtime.InteropServices.Guid("C1468187-3DA1-49df-ADF8-5F8600E59EA8")]
public interface IParseText
Attributes
ComVisibleAttribute GuidAttribute

Methods

Parse(String, IErrorHandler)

When implemented in a class, parses the specified source code.

public void Parse (string code, Microsoft.JScript.IErrorHandler error);
Parameters
code
String

The source code to parse.

error
IErrorHandler

An object that contains information about errors that occur when code is being parsed.
